00:24:48.896 --> 00:24:52.836
countries. But if we don't continue to push on this,

419
00:24:53.356 --> 00:24:57.116
HPV vaccine uptake and screening when

420
00:24:57.176 --> 00:25:00.936
possible will drive how fast we achieve

421
00:25:01.016 --> 00:25:04.906
these goals. So again, high uptake is what is needed,

